    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Toni Helminen</b>\n</p><p><b>Toni Helminen</b>, (JohnWoe)<br />\na Finnish IT freelancer, and computer games and computer chess programmer. He is author of multiple <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source</a> chess and chess variant engines <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>,\nthe <a href=\"/Shogi\" title=\"Shogi\">Shogi</a> engine <a href=\"/index.php?title=RubyShogi&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"RubyShogi (page does not exist)\">RubyShogi</a>, the chess variant engine <a href=\"/index.php?title=Shuriken&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Shuriken (page does not exist)\">Shuriken</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gothic_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gothic Chess (page does not exist)\">Gothic Chess</a>  engine <a href=\"/index.php?title=Havoc&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Havoc (page does not exist)\">Havoc</a>, and the chess playing engines <a href=\"/Sapeli\" title=\"Sapeli\">Sapeli</a> and <a href=\"/Mayhem\" title=\"Mayhem\">Mayhem</a>, the latter featuring <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2019\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2019</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Toni_Helminen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Toni Helminen</a> (<b>2022</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/SamuraiDangyo/lazy-sorting-algorithm\">Lazy sorting algorithm</a></i>. <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Toni_Helminen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2019\">2019</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Toni_Helminen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2019\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=70815\">Eucalyptus - KPK Bitbases Generator</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 24, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/KPK\" title=\"KPK\">KPK</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=70534\">Sapeli 1.0 - New chess engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 20, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71365\">Shuriken, a Ruby chess variant engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 25, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71549\">RubyShogi 0.1</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 14, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71550\">Shogi Perft numbers</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 14, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Shogi\" title=\"Shogi\">Shogi</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72248\">luataxx, an Ataxx engine written in Lua</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 04, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=72669\">LastEmperor - Chess960 perft tool</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 28, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess960_Perft_Results\" title=\"Chess960 Perft Results\">Chess960 Perft Results</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Toni_Helminen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73347\">frcGen - Chess960 tool</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 13, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73576\">New Musketeer engine: Capitaine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 06, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75500\">Mayhem NNUE - New NN engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 22, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=76576\">Havoc - New Gothic chess engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=76592\">C++ type system AKA what is exactly int&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 14, 2021</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=77142\">Thread overhead in C++</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 21, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">Thread</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=79279\">Lazy sorting algorithm - Sorting on steroids</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2022 </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Toni_Helminen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/toni-helminen-ab47691a2/\">Toni Helminen | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/SamuraiDangyo\">SamuraiDangyo (Toni Helminen) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://samuraigames1.itch.io/\">samuraigames1 - itch.io</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Toni_Helminen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/SamuraiDangyo\">SamuraiDangyo (Toni Helminen) · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75500\">Mayhem NNUE - New NN engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">JohnWoe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 22, 2020</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"refe